text: The Ambassador of Malaysia to the State of Qatar is the head of Malaysia's diplomatic mission to Qatar. The position has the rank and status of an Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary and is based in the Embassy of Malaysia, Doha. ==List of heads of mission== ===Ambassadors to Qatar=== {| class=wikitable !
